      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778954927665,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n-------------------------------------\n- Riders should be able to enter pickup and drop location and get an estimated fare\n- Based on the estimated fare riders should request for a ride\n- upon request, riders should find nearby drivers\n- drivers should accept/decline the request and navigate to pickup/drop loaction\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n-------------------------------------\n- Riders should be able to enter pickup and drop location and get an estimated fare\n- Based on the estimated fare riders should request for a ride\n- upon request, riders should find nearby drivers\n- drivers should accept/decline the request and navigate to pickup/drop loaction\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yGYXccOz1o7pWvdIuz6U7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1084.978125450303,
      "y": 72.81618797628582,
      "width": 977.8524536896457,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1895997120,
      "version": 658,
      "versionNonce": 592115392,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1778954936952,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-Functional Requirements\n---------------------------------------------\n- Should be low latency to match the request\n- should be strongly consistent for in ride matching, preventing no driver should be getting the\nmultiple request simutaneously\n- should be highly throughput during peak times",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-Functional Requirements\n---------------------------------------------\n- Should be low latency to match the request\n- should be strongly consistent for in ride matching, preventing no driver should be getting the multiple request simutaneously\n- should be highly throughput during peak times",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
