      "text": "\nAPi's\n--------------------\n1. POST /fare \n\nBody {\n            pickup location\n            drop Location\n        }\n\nRes {\n        fairId\n        estimatedFare\n        eta\n        ....\n      }\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
